text: John Henry Francis "Jack" Synon (28 July 1924 – 4 February 2015) was an Australian rules footballer who played for the Collingwood Football Club in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * Category:1924 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players
